<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en" dir="ltr">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.5.0/css/bootstrap.min.css" integrity="sha384-9aIt2nRpC12Uk9gS9baDl411NQApFmC26EwAOH8WgZl5MYYxFfc+NcPb1dKGj7Sk" crossorigin="anonymous">
    <title>Home</title>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="border border-dark rounded mx-5 mt-5 p-4">
      <h1 class='text-center'><strong >Routes</strong></h1>
      <br><br>
      <ul>
        <li>
          Route for address page:- <mark>/:userId/addresses</mark><br>
          Ex:- <br>
          Checkout Addresses for <a href="/1/addresses">userId 1</a>, <a href="/2/addresses">userId 2</a>
        </li>
        <br><br>
        <li>
          Route for address form:- /:userId/addresses/form<br>
          Ex:- <br>
          Fill address form for <a href="/1/addresses/form">userId 1</a>, <a href="/2/addresses/form">userId 2</a>
        </li>
        <br><br>
        <li>Route for location of user:- /getlocation<br>
          Ex:- <br>
          <div class="alert alert-warning my-2">
            Requires API_KEY configuration in backend for these to work.
          </div>
          Location for coords <a href="/getlocation?latLong=23.2599,77.4126">23.2599° N, 77.4126° E</a>
        </li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
